high_descs: Turn right and walk to the white toilet on the right.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle from the right side of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk to the white dresser on the left.
Put the spray bottle in front of the middle box of tissues on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place a spray bottle on a dresser.

high_descs: Turn to the right and right again to face the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle from the toilet tank.
Carry the bottle and turn right. Then turn left to face the counter.
Place the bottle on the counter in front of the box of tissues.
anns.task_desc: Move a bottle to the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the toilet
Pick up the yellow spray bottle that is sitting on the back of the toilet
Turn right and head to the bathtub, then make a left and face the long counter with the drawers
Place the spray bottle on the counter in front of the tissue box in the middle
anns.task_desc: Place a spray bottle on a counter
